      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im looking into opening a small coffee shop in a rural area where rent and living costs are pretty low. i'm seeing news about these new minimum wage hikes being proposed. how do these kinds of laws usually play out for small businesses in places like that?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
